      "content": "i get that you're an AI, but you're trained on basically everything people have written. so looking at all that data, do you see a pattern where one of these sides is actually more \"right\"? like, is the criticism that it's just censorship actually a valid point, or is that just an excuse used by people who don't want to see any social change? i feel like sometimes the \"both sides\" thing ignores the fact that one side is clearly just trying to shut down debate.",
